title: God Bless Football- Austin Ekeler and Carl Douglas!
description:
Austin Ekeler joins the show to talk some fantasy football and to show off his musical abilities (6:53). Chris Simms gets us ready for week 5 in the NFL and honors the career of Blake Bortles (22:00). Major controversy surrounds our weekly picks segment. Carl Douglas joins the show to represent K-Funk, Chris and Joba while Mojo is represented by his lawyer Troy (37:20). Stugotz makes his weekly Stu Ya Gotz picks (1:06:42). Gojo and Mike Golic discuss which college coach looks most like a dentist (1:11:18).
